snippet.title: Is Amber Heard’s Surprise Baby Safe With Her?
snippet.description: What is the responsibility of a parent and a surrogate? Should we really be comfortable with Amber Heard being a single mother based on her past demonstrations of her disturbing, abusive “stress management” style? That is what I ponder in this video. If you want to hear Amber explain in her own words how stress makes her violent towards those closest to her listen to this https://youtu.be/aca0KWoHtqQ.
